title: Week 8 Recap (with Kyle Brandt)!!
itunes:title: Week 8 Recap (with Kyle Brandt)!!
description:
Rachel Bonnetta and company are back for a brand new episode of Benched with Bonnetta! To start, Rachel is joined by Kyle Brandt and they recap what went into their awesome Halloween costumes and they pick the NFL personalities they'd want to have with them for a night out (2:30). After the break, Rachel looks ahead to Thursday night's game between the Eagles and Texans (12:55). Finally, Rachel tells you the best and worst thing she saw this week, and she tries not to get emotional about this one (17:42).    

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
